Package eu.mihosoft.freerouting.geometry.planar

Class OrthogonalBoundingDirections

java.lang.Object
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.geometry.planar.OrthogonalBoundingDirections
All Implemented Interfaces:
ShapeBoundingDirections
public class OrthogonalBoundingDirections extends Object implements ShapeBoundingDirections
Implements the abstract class ShapeDirections as the 4 orthogonal directions. The class is a singleton with the only instanciation INSTANCE.
